  div.element-doc
    div.title
      h5 2FA authentication
    div.about
      p TBD
    div.preview
      div.item
        section.pl-account.sign-in
          div.welcome 2-Step Verification
          div.lead.
            Enter the verification code generated by your 2FA authenticator application.
          form.pl-form.pl-validate(data-ruleset="user_2fa")
            div
              label(for="2fa_code") Code from authenticator app
              input.pl-input.code(name="code", id="2fa_code", type="text", autocomplete="off", placeholder="Enter code", minlength=6, maxlength=6)
            div
              button.pl-button.submit.with-icon(type="submit")
                include ../static/2fa.svg
                | Verify
            div.pl-text-micro.copy.
              If, for any reason, you cannot access your authenticator application for your two-factor
              verification code, you can log in using your recovery code.
              Each recovery code can be used only once.
            div.links
              div.link
                | Need help accessing your account?
                |
                a(href="#") Contact support
